{"id": 1423, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得有哪些新时代为人父母的礼节？", "description": "一言以蔽之，是“善待周围的人”。（题图来自：Riikka Laakso）", "record_count": 6026, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170103145655scPk9GTNOmzWhQYq.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-04T03:00:07Z", "options": [{"id": 150528, "content": "别催婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313210}, {"id": 150529, "content": "在外面要有素质", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890655}, {"id": 152834, "content": "我丁克 哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902089}, {"id": 150531, "content": "发动态能不能别每次都是3×3来5组的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 381914}, {"id": 150788, "content": "任何情况下在孩子面前能控制自己的情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891858}, {"id": 151556, "content": "由于很多家长在孩子不情愿时，无论是否因为孩子的无赖任性，强行带孩子离开，使我们已经分不清拐卖绑架孩子的行为和家长教育孩子的行为。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895247}, {"id": 153349, "content": "不在朋友圈晒娃，拼团购奶粉，拿小孩当头像的家长", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903353}, {"id": 150534, "content": "别让孩子模仿父母说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890668}, {"id": 150790, "content": "以好好管教孩子，代替“他还是个孩子”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891850}, {"id": 151303, "content": "不以“怎么和孩子一般见识”或者“只是个孩子”这种言辞来纵容孩子变成无法无天的熊孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893763}, {"id": 150536, "content": "给孩子留面子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890691}, {"id": 157960, "content": "和现在的小孩相比突然觉得自己小时候就是个傻白甜的小傻纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914673}, {"id": 150537, "content": "答应孩子的事情要做到，不要信口开河", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890691}, {"id": 150539, "content": "待人温和，不要大喊大叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889355}, {"id": 150540, "content": "平等倾听孩子的诉求，你要主观打断孩子的奇思妙想", "image": "img/option/option/2017010420073036aPV9xRFEJA80hI.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 888554}, {"id": 150796, "content": "尊重孩子的选择", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891868}, {"id": 150541, "content": "教孩子说谢谢和对不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889520}, {"id": 151565, "content": "不要总因为自己的经验就认为孩子做什么都是冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349453}, {"id": 155405, "content": "理解并支持你的孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905010}, {"id": 150542, "content": "别带孩子去咖啡馆，需要安静的地方都别", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890721}, {"id": 150544, "content": "各种晒娃照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649741}, {"id": 151057, "content": "把ta当作思想独立的个体，尊重ta。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892799}, {"id": 151315, "content": "不要和孩子开玩笑；在认识上不要秉持＂自己即公理＂的原则约束孩子；", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 873028}, {"id": 150807, "content": "不管见到谁都要叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891909}, {"id": 151323, "content": "家长自己得三观正，告诉小孩什么是对的，什么是错的，什么能做，什么不能做，别在外害人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806022}, {"id": 150556, "content": "不要让孩子养成衣来伸手，饭来张口的坏习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890802}, {"id": 150557, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865474}, {"id": 151325, "content": "尊重孩子的选择，进孩子房间要敲门。让孩子在家有遮风避雨的感觉。有些事可以不去做，但该会的必须会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890395}, {"id": 150558, "content": "哈哈大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865474}, {"id": 152094, "content": "别认为每个人都该惯着你孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886359}, {"id": 150559, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865474}, {"id": 150815, "content": "不管怎样、趁着孩子孩子还在你身边、请多陪陪他，不要等到长大以后。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891965}, {"id": 151327, "content": "尊重孩子的选择，进孩子房间要敲门。让孩子在家有遮风避雨的感觉。有些事可以不去做，但该会的必须会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890395}, {"id": 150817, "content": "不要为了自己的私欲，带着孩子去看不适合的电影。首先，中国电影还未分级，其次，孩子不想看，你还要求他在漆黑的密闭空间2h时长之久保持安静？影响其他观众观影感受都是其次了??‍♀️", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891986}, {"id": 151841, "content": "多陪伴有个美好的童年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896963}, {"id": 152098, "content": "平等的朋友关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892334}, {"id": 150819, "content": "为什么给我和谐了啊？影响社会主义发展了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891986}, {"id": 151588, "content": "平等的对待孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853037}, {"id": 154661, "content": "千万别说 这是为了你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906789}, {"id": 150823, "content": "我觉得这个观点没啥问题", "image": "img/option/option/201701051439375AzI34vnwdVhJOfR.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891986}, {"id": 151591, "content": "不在别人面前让自家孩子过分谦虚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 371475}, {"id": 150057, "content": "朋友圈晒娃频率维持在每周两次以下", "image": null, "praise_count": 246, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 150569, "content": "性教育并不是件羞于启齿的事，你现在不讲，以后你的孩子可能会做出真正让你羞于启齿的事情都不一定。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214251}, {"id": 164649, "content": "教会孩子餐桌礼仪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931186}, {"id": 150058, "content": "除了低幼动画，不要问“这部电影适合带孩子看吗”…都不适合", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 150570, "content": "别让你家小孩毁坏公物。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214251}, {"id": 150059, "content": "不要拿孩子照片做头像，群聊里根本看不出谁是谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 278, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 150060, "content": "坐飞机火车的时候带够食物、玩具等安抚用品", "image": null, "praise_count": 337, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 150573, "content": "挣钱养娃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889345}, {"id": 151341, "content": "不要因为孩子脾气暴躁为原因，疏于对孩子的管理。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893892}]}